title: Fresh Blood: What Lies South...
description: Jake Davis, Colt Ward, and Kain Daly escape from the June gloom of southern California and decide to head far south. From 20ft crocs to the Cory Lopez grind off the groms are ready for anything! All happening in good timing for the US Champs... we think their chance of winning has increased after spending some time in the warm waters of Central America.
